<doc id="1131879" wikidata="Q8019386" url="?curid=1131879" title="William Thornberry">
<text>William Thornberry is the name of:

*William McClellan &quot;Mac&quot; Thornberry (b. 1958), U.S. Representative from Texas (1995–present)
*William Homer Thornberry (1909–1995), U.S. Representative from Texas (1945–1963) and federal judge</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q539444" start="55" end="81" title="Mac Thornberry" label="&amp;quot;Mac&amp;quot; Thornberry"/>
