*&quot;A Star Called Cyrene&quot; (aka &quot;Seventy Light-Years from Sol&quot;) (1966)
*&quot;The Angry Mountain&quot; (1970)
*&quot;Talk with the Animals&quot; (1970)
*&quot;Allison, Carmichael and Tattersall&quot; (1970)
*&quot;The Mad Scientist and The FBI&quot; (1970)
