<text>Winchester-on-the-Severn is a populated place located in Anne Arundel County, Maryland, United States.

Winchester-on-the-Severn is tied with Washington-on-the-Brazos, Texas, at 21 letters for the title of longest hyphenated placename in the United States appearing in the US Geological Survey&#x27;s Geographic Names Information System.

